      "title": "Until the litro gas arrives",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Until the gas arrives at the Badulla Litro Gas Agency, customers have been queuing up empty cylinders for 20 days.",
        "Hundreds of empty cylinders brought in daily by customers queuing up were tied up in front of the company until gas was delivered."
      ],
